185/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pathophysiology+and+therapy+of+chronic+radiation-induced+injury+to+the+colon&amp;author=CS+Donner&amp;publication_year=1998&amp;journal=Dig+Dis&amp;pages=253-261&amp;doi=10.1159%2F000016873&amp;pmid=9732185">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">28.</div><div id="r28" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Hoeffel C, Crema MD, Belkacem A, et al. Multi–detector row CT: spectrum of diseases involving the ileocecal area. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2006;26(5):1373–1390.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.265045191">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16973770/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Multi%E2%80%93detector+row+CT%3A+spectrum+of+diseases+involving+the+ileocecal+area&amp;author=C+Hoeffel&amp;author=MD+Crema&amp;author=A+Belkacem&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1373-1390&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.265045191&amp;pmid=16973770">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">29.</div><div id="r29" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Sugimura K, Okizuka H. Postsurgical pelvis: treatment follow-up. <em>Radiol Clin North Am</em> 2002;40(3):659–680, viii.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0033-8389(01)00016-1">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12117198/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Postsurgical+pelvis%3A+treatment+follow-up&amp;author=K+Sugimura&amp;